mixin BottomBlock({jsDisabled})
	-
		const baseClasses = 'w-full text-xl font-medium'
		const additionalClasses = jsDisabled ? '' : ' fixed z-0 bottom-0'
		const blockClasses = baseClasses + additionalClasses

	.bottomBlock(class=blockClasses)
		div(class="md:container mx-auto py-6 px-4 lg:px-5 text-center")
			p.mx-auto.mb-4
				| Landing page example. Created using the BEM methodology. I used the tailwind library to add a basic style. The project was built with Gulp.js.
			a(class="text-black" href="https://ustymenko.vercel.app")
				| Back to portfolio